SCO warriors destroy the equipment and the location of the enemy's aerial reconnaissance in Kherson region.

About thisinformsCommand of Special Operations forces of the Armed Forces of Ukraine.

As it is noted, the operators of the Maritime Center of the SPP named after the Cossack chieftain Antin Golovaty found a building with aero -intelligence, the station of the IIT, the ALIENTECH antenna and the enemy BC.

“The FPV-Aye operators were involved in the enemy's personnel and equipment and the calculation of 122 mm howitzers D-30, whichSurgically accurateThey destroyed all the goals, ”the message reads.

The department also added that the estimated losses of the enemy amounted to about 5 people.

As reported by the Armyinform, special forces dronesDestroyedmortar position and 5 invaders.
